"EP-SVA70MB-01" appears to be silkscreened on the removable ''[[Atheros]]'' wireless module. :The RAM chip P/N for the wireless module may be HY5DU561622ETP-D43 (32MB).
===Specifications=== :;Specs from the FCC manual.. *14 Megapixel camera, shoots 1080p video @30fps *180 degree super wide angle field of view *JPEG format photos *AAC audio compression w/ AGC *Up to 32GB microSD cards supported *Average recording time of 4 hours (using 32GB microSD card in 1080p30/720p60) *USB 2.0 Host (for charging and data transfer), HDMI, AV/Composite *1200mAh Li-ion battery, approx. 2 hours w/o Wi-Fi or 1 hour w/ Wi-Fi PODZ *Waterproof at a depth up to 10 meters *Dimension: 40mm x 40mm x 108mm *Weight: ~127.8g (w/ PODZ), ~133.2g (w/ Wi-Fi PODZ)
